assets_margin_mode_multi_support_desc:
Please note:
Users can transfer the above assets into the Futures Account as margin;
In the multi-assets mode, certain assets used as margin in multi-asset mode will receive a value haircut. For example, in the multi-assets mode, the collateral value of BTC with a market value of 1000{coin} is 950{coin}, the collateral value of ETH with a market value of 1000{coin} is 950{coin};
In the multi-assets mode, all funds are evaluated according to their own valuation converted into the proportion of {coin} (i.e. Account Equity), which allows traders to use any asset that can be transferred into the Futures Account as collateral, thus avoiding the need for frequent currency exchanges and the additional loss, improving funds utilization rate
